data.title: John E “Cowboy” Schubmehl (1949
data.meta_description: John E. Cowboy Schubmehl, age 65, passed away peacefully Tuesday March 24, 2015 at Corning Hospital.  Cowboy was born June 24, 1949 in Wayland, a son of Glenn & Ruth (Lander) Schubmehl. He was a US Marine veteran of the Vietnam War serving from 1968 to 1974. He was a former sandblaster for TTA in Hornell.  Cowboy was a...
